    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <p> Is 10 numeric digits in length. The tenth digit is a check digit used to confirm its validity. The check digit is validated using the Modulus 11 algorithm and the use of this algorithm is mandatory. </p>

            <strong >Step 1</strong>
            Multiply each of the first nine digits by a weighting factor as follows:
